node.text:
Remembering those who made the ultimate sacrifice.. I dedicate this flag for the people we lost on 9/11 and also the men and women who served in the military and/or has given the ultimate sacrifice for the USA. Thank you. Next time you’re near Mount Antero, look up and you’ll see the flag we hiked up and planted! 
(Full video soon)

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Scuba Jake in Columbus, Georgia with @speedousa. May be an image of 1 person and body of water.

node.text:
#ad I #MakeWaves by finding the treasure that lies beneath them.

Being a modern-day treasure hunter has afforded me the opportunity to explore the unknown, help others be reunited with their lost valuables, and find my true calling in life.

Treasure hunting has also allowed me to connect with so many people across the world, and I try my best to influence others to be the best version of themselves by being honest and compassionate in my work.  I have learned that even small impacts can help influence the world by affecting change with my followers. @SpeedoUSA makes it possible for me to inspire others to search the unknown, help the environment, and hunt for their passion in life. 

How do you #makewaves? Let me know in the comments below.
